Package food

Class Subscribe

java.lang.Object
food.Subscribe
public class Subscribe extends Object
Represents a subscription entity, encapsulating details about a subscription. This class includes properties for subscription ID, user ID, food item ID, and creation time.
Author:
Shuting Wang
